Directus validate all input data except the related data.

Known bug: Adding a file to a related field doesn't validate the required fields.

Example:

`image` is a `file` type Field.
```
{
  "image": {"data": "<base64-content>"}
}
```

It will throw an error trying to write a file with the name of "" (empty string).

